Package com.smartcar.sdk

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SmartcarCallback
    Callback interface that should be implemented by the application.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SmartcarAuth
    Main class that provides SDK access methods.
    SmartcarCodeReceiver
    Activity that receives the response sent to the custom URL scheme defined by the application.
    SmartcarResponse
    Class that encompasses the response code and error message, if any.
    WebViewActivity
    Activity that sets up a WebView and manages the URL loading.
